data.description: Available Now! Very nice 3Bed/2.5Bath home located in Northwoods Estates in close proximity to shopping, dining, and interstate. Inside features a spacious Family Room with fireplace and hardwood floors. Kitchen offers plenty of cabinets and counter space, black and stainless appliances, and an eat-in area. Large Master with private bath and walk-in closet. Laundry Room with washer/dryer hookups. Outside features a screened in porch overlooking a large privacy fenced back yard, perfect for entertaining! One car garage with built in work space. This home won't last long...call today!
